    "YangsThoughts": "Yet another antique in my mechbay, this time a Clan Ghost Bear bodyguard mech. But I don't recognize those arm weapons, some sort of weird lbx autocannon mixed with a gauss rifle? The clans don't like bodyguarding much, so they retired this design relatively quickly. This mech is very slow, so you'll need to upgrade the engine if you want any sort of reasonable speed, but it's extremely well armed with long and short range weapons and well armored, so if you can get enemies to come into range you can put them down fast."
